    Wave 5-F handler addition. Depends on 118R (migrated playbook so the workspace tab actually has composed state). Pattern precedent: task 092 wired 8 R6 handlers into the same seed script — mirror that approach exactly for the row entry. The handler is read-only by design — promotion to T3/T4 cross-session memory remains gated by R6 task 094/095 approval UX (NFR-A1 explicit promotion). Architecture §11.1 is binding: do NOT rebuild `WorkspaceStateService`; reuse it.
